name: Tusken Breath Mask
Lore: 'Sand People use a special mask to reclaim exhaled moisture in the hot, harsh environment of Tatooine. Protects by filtering blowing sand and dispersing excess heat.',
Text: 'Deploy on any Tatooine site where you have just won a battle. Target one of your characters not at Tatooine. Upon reaching, target takes mask. While on Tatooine, target''s power and forfeit are +2 and has immunity to attrition of exactly 3.',
